<span class="ruby">在这里这些观众里还有他妈的狄瓦！<span class="rt">We got a lotta fuckin Daeva in this here crowd!</span></span></p>
<p><span class="ruby">数百万死灵都在收容之中<span class="rt">Billions of dead souls inside containment</span></span><br />
<span class="ruby">我们要做什么？（阻止基地组织！）<span class="rt">What we gonna do? (Stop Al-Qaeda!)</span></span><br />
<span class="ruby">在墙上在地板底部有个洞<span class="rt">There’s a hole in the wall in the bottom of the floor</span></span><br />
